{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act26side", "eventName": "空想花庭", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HE-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "我曾捨命為你", "storyInfo": "一場突如其來的大火打斷了費德里科的追蹤。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g11_monasterycorridor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有一點驚訝。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我終究背叛了信仰嗎？", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#7$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因為你的逃避，斯特凡諾。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道你是否是受到了什麼外物的影響，如果......", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有如果，奧盧斯。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還不至於受源石技藝影響。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時轉變我們想法的並不一定是源石技藝。有太多東西足以影響我們，斯特凡諾。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你在勸我重新考慮。為什麼，異教的教士。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今我的決定，難道不是你想要看到的？", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能否認。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我也得承認，在這座了不起的建築尚在伊比利亞時，我曾有幸在此學習，那段時光對於那時的我來說彌足珍貴。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯特凡諾，在這方面我同你一樣。我對這裡同樣懷有感情。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得那位和你一起從拉特蘭來的修士。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得許多人。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你記得的那個人，在六十年前帶上他的銃，決定和當時的國教會共進退，而我......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我選擇留下，保護剩下的人。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以此為信念，堅持至今。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你清楚，你仍要我繼續等待，繼續忍耐？", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你現在要否認你一直宣揚的那些，轉而要我斟酌，勸我堅定？", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然不。斯特凡諾，當然不。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，正因我行走在我認為正確的路上，便希望你也如此。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天早上，如果你仍然堅持，那麼我便認為這就是你的選擇。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會準備好你需要的東西。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你還沒有想好，我會勸你繼續考慮。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論如何......我希望你的決定發自真心。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......奧盧斯，你弄錯了一件事。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#3$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已別無選擇。", "name": "修道院主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_923_1#2$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，如果真是如此......", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼我會歡迎你，斯特凡諾，我新的同胞。", "name": "奧盧斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_941_1#2$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g9_monasteryroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "介意我進來嗎？"