es": {"content": "和你們提到我的人在哪？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_929_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大哥哥，看起來好兇......", "name": "艾絲塔拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_929_1#2$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_928_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好兇哦！而且大哥哥都不說自己的名字......沒有禮貌！", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_928_1#5$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_929_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽說過，不可以回答不知道名字的陌生人的問題......", "name": "艾絲塔拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_929_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_929_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兇兇的費德里科哥哥，是好人嗎......？", "name": "艾絲塔拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_929_1#7$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_928_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "肯定是好人！就像故事裡說的那樣~", "name": "艾倫戴爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_928_1#3$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_929_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那、那可以說了吧？", "name": "艾絲塔拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_929_1#7$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes"